11. O-O
11. h5 {This is the key idea to avoid any problems on the kingside.It would have been careless to play11...Be7and allow12.g4!Nh413.Nxh4Bxh414.g5!when our dark-squared bishop is stuck.} 
12. Be3
12. Be7
13. Bf2
13. O-O
14. h3
