17. Nf1 {I am not saying that you will encounter this maneuver, but the computer likes it.} 
17. f5 {This move is quite important so we can get rid of the doubled pawns and avoid a passive defense.} 
18. b3
18. f4 {With enough activity to compensate for the ruined queenside structure.} 
