6. h3
6. Bxf3
7. Nxf3
7. Nc6
8. c3
8. e6 {Staying flexible. Now most people will continue with9.d4, but the computer finds the somewhat tricky variation starting with9.h4!?Bg710.d4h511.a3Qb612.b4cxd413.cxd4a614.Bd3Nh6!15.Be3Ng4with a close to equal game.} 
9. d4
9. cxd4
